casebody.data:
First Department,

July, 1939.

(July 11, 1939.) Josephine B. Campbell, Appellant, v. John J. Campbell, Jr., and Others, Respondents. (Action to Set Aside Conveyances.)

Order reversed, with ten dollars costs and disbursements, and motion to dismiss complaint denied. No opinion. Present — Martin, P. J., O’Malley, Glennon, Cohn and Callahan, JJ.; O’Malley and Glennon, JJ., dissent and vote to affirm.
